{"tid":1719174,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好理民唔民意啦！","createTime":"2019-11-14T04:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T06:12:28.000Z","uid":216662,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eef63510c982f01b80a39cb5a20f279841e68b86","tid":1719174,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"發夢一定要Keep住快閃開花！<br />\n<br />\n開頭啲人當然會話示威者搞搞震阻搵食，但當真係冇得搵食之後唔淨只會埋怨示威者，一定會埋怨埋政府！<br />\n<br />\n攬炒就緊㗎啦！<br />\n到越來越多藍絲廢佬都出嚟搞事嗰陣，佢地都只會係阻揾食既一份子，佢地彈出我地就彈入，佢地唔出我地就出，所以一定一定要快閃！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nkeep住快閃開花！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d736678d8c546ba6349f1dc4cab9bf85f16497","tid":1719174,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f54abb6f321123f478456653f910d6d1d5b2b2ae","tid":1719174,"uid":308531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeSdphW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeSdphW.jpg&h=9e433e02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dce1f86c970ef6df83952765d70e84ec05604e69","tid":1719174,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a0d540abe84953cc0d07bf0b1a1ed7efff2c2a","tid":1719174,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i